---
import GridCard from './GridCard.astro';
---

<GridCard id="contact-me">
	<div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
		<h2 class="font-bold text-2xl font-sans">Contact Me</h2>

		<div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
			<h3 class="font-bold text-sm">Raymond Kneipp</h3>
			<p class="max-w-screen-md p-3 bg-stone-800 mr-6">
				Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Doloribus
				suscipit totam dolores ea expedita, facilis fuga iusto ut aut minima a
				optio. Nulla modi voluptas facere illo! Dolore, neque nesciunt.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="flex flex-col items-end gap-1 ml-auto max-w-screen-md">
			<h3 class="font-bold text-sm">Person</h3>
			<p class="p-3 bg-amber-400 text-stone-900 ml-6">
				Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Necessitatibus
				deserunt porro fugit eum consequatur, eos officia placeat quidem ad est
				voluptate veritatis excepturi id recusandae rerum, dolorem inventore hic
				voluptatum?
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
			<h3 class="font-bold text-sm">Raymond Kneipp</h3>
			<div
				class="p-3 pt-4 bg-stone-800 w-min flex gap-1 justify-center items-center"
			>
				<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-stone-400 rounded-full animate-bounce"></div>
				<div
					class="w-2 h-2 bg-stone-400 rounded-full animate-bounce"
					style="animation-delay: 250ms;"
				>
				</div>
				<div
					class="w-2 h-2 bg-stone-400 rounded-full animate-bounce"
					style="animation-delay: 500ms"
				>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
				<h3 class="font-bold text-sm">Raymond Kneipp</h3>
				<p class="max-w-screen-md w-fit p-3 bg-stone-800 mr-6">
					Thank you for reaching out. I will be getting back to you as soon as I
					can!
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</GridCard>
